question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-47", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 47, "raw_text": "47. 根據本文，下列句意說明何者正確？         1.莫之與「京」：齊等\n    (A)亦寄酒為跡者也――有酒之處必有陶淵明蹤跡\n    (B)抑揚爽朗，莫之與京――文章起伏跌宕、清朗通達，無人能及\n    (C)干青雲而直上――志向遠大，在仕途上也曾飛黃騰達\n    (D)尚想其德，恨不同時――感嘆自己德行高潔卻生不逢時\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-107-chinese-048", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-107-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據本文，無法得知下列何者？", "options": ["陶淵明詩多以酒為寫作題材", "陶淵明詩文在當時獨樹一格", "作者對陶淵明極為欣賞崇敬", "後世文壇深受陶淵明的影響 13             試題結束"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-107-chinese-passage-47", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2d7d32b90c63", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05a67d1d6082", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 48, "raw_text": "48. 根據本文，無法得知下列何者？\n    (A)陶淵明詩多以酒為寫作題材\n    (B)陶淵明詩文在當時獨樹一格\n    (C)作者對陶淵明極為欣賞崇敬\n    (D)後世文壇深受陶淵明的影響\n\n\n\n\n                      13             試題結束\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}]'::jsonb) AS t(
